<P>7 Through all his Book like some great <HI>Com|manders</HI>
or <HI>Generals</HI> by Land or Sea,<NOTE PLACE="marg">The inju<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="tech" EXTENT="2 letters">|ing &amp; wild im|periousness of <HI>G. Fox.</HI></NOTE> yea like the
<HI>Emperors</HI> or <HI>Dictators</HI> among the <HI>Romanes,</HI> so doth
this wild devouring Soul give forth his high and
