Government</HI> of <HI>God</HI> and Christ in the Soul. <HI>Secondly,</HI>
The Government of God in his holy Providence in
the World. 3. His Government in the <HI>Congregation</HI> or
<HI>Churches</HI> of his <HI>Saints</HI> called out the World.
<HI>Fourthly,</HI> the <HI>glorious State</HI> to come af<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="tech" EXTENT="2 letters">r this Life:
He knowes that his <HI>Iourney man</HI> G. <HI>Fox</HI> is<NOTE N="5" PLACE="foot">Erase the parenthesis, and insert "a." <HI>R. W. Ms. Ann.</HI></NOTE> (fit In|strument
