<P><PB N="379" REF="196">
The Lord Jesus knowing that not the <HI>Phar<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="tech" EXTENT="1 letter">sees</HI>
alone <HI>&amp;c.</HI> but the <HI>Iews</HI> generally also, and his own
