<P>As <HI>First,</HI> that a pardon is certainly come, <HI>Secondly,</HI>
that my <HI>Name</HI> is in it, my <HI>deliverance</HI> and <HI>Salvation</HI>
is wrapt up in it The great <HI>King of Heaven</HI> (like
<HI>Ahashuerosh</HI>) his <HI>Ange<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="tech" EXTENT="1 letter"></HI> is ev<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="tech" EXTENT="1 letter">r: now he hath
thoughts of <HI>marriage Loves</HI> and <HI>Ioyes,</HI> and <HI>Sec|ondly,</HI>
I (though a <HI>poor Captive Iew, poor Esther</HI>)
I am she his Eye hath fixt on, and his Soul de|lights
in:</P>
<P><HI>3dly,</HI> I askt what preaching is, but the publishing
