<HI>Answer,</HI> this is something, but reacheth not home,
for, if all the men in the world have this <HI>Light</HI>
(which is s<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="tech" EXTENT="1 letter">fficient without hearing) why should
not some, (especially the wise and Enquirours, &amp;c.)
