he had heard something, (and because God had
a purpose to make Extraordinary use of him, an
Extraordinary hand from Heaven humbling and
preparing him to publish or preach unto the Na|tions.</P>
<P>The 21 <HI>Instance,</HI><NOTE PLACE="marg">80 Tko. Pollard.</NOTE> is in <HI>pag.</HI> 80. where G. <HI>Fox</HI>
brings in <HI>Tho. Pollard,</HI> saying, <HI>[To say the Officers of
