To <HI>Kings,</HI> To their <HI>houses</HI> and <HI>Palaces,</HI> yea, to
<HI>Armes</HI> with <HI>Banners,</HI> &amp;c.</P>
<P>4. Although the <HI>Lord Major</HI> of <HI>London,</HI> and the
several Officers of the City are not made and or|dained
in the public Streets, nor <HI>Generals</HI> and other
