<P>Wee may make a stand here and observe three
things.<NOTE PLACE="marg">Whab Grace it is that Pa|pists Ar|minians and Fox|ians Fall from.</NOTE></P>
<P>1. The <HI>horrible abuse of Gods Excellent Gifts</HI> of
